
=== OVD Windows slave server generator ===

I. Software dependencies

	* Python 2.5
		* py2exe
		* pywin32
		* pysvn
		* twisted
	* Java 2.5 jdk
		* ant
	* Mingw gcc
		* make
	* nsis
		* nsis PassDialog plugin (http://nsis.sourceforge.net/PassDialog_plug-in)
	
	* GNU Gettext
	
	* Visual Studio 2008
		* map C:\Program Files\Microsoft Visual Studio 9.0\VC\vcpackages

	* DDK
		* add ddk bin dir to PATH
		* add env var WINDDK_PATH
		* add gs libs to DDK libs dir


	All the software directories have to be defined in the %PATH% 
	variable in order to be able to launch gcc, make, python, 
	java ... from anywhere on the system



II. Download the code and binaries
        Setup gs-x86 and gs-amd64 using ghostscript according ro the README in ApplicationServer/Windows/Printer


IV. Compile

	makeServer.py clean all install
